EmitterModeHeader.ModeComment: RF every pulse group rather than every 10 pulses, due to the tediousness of programming that pattern in CEESIM and due to not switching carrier RF during a FSK sequence (which isn't typical)

Generator.GeneratorComment: HPRF Dwell & Switch w/ 3-Stage FMR (Unmod -> 10 kHz -> 90 kHz)(Some dwells have an invisible pulse to fill out a 10 ms subframe time). Varying 13-Bit BPSK PW's. 4-Bar/4-Level Electronic Raster, 3 Subframes per Beam Position.
Single PRI Dwell (invisible pulse to fill out 10 ms subframe), 3-Stage FMR (Unmod -> 100 kHz -> -55 kHz), Unmod 0.5 usec PW, steady stare scan for 3 subframes (interrupting once per frame, 50 ms)
